attributionInfo.brokerName: Main Street Realty of Pueblo, Inc

data.description: Beautiful new ranch style home on a large 1 acre lot in Pueblo West. Space between neighbors and a huge backyard! Enter the home to see a spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and an eat-in kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, pantry, bar seating, dining room and walk-out to the backyard. The private master bedroom has its own 5-pc bathroom attached and a walk-in closet. The other 2 additional bedrooms have their own full bathroom as well. The laundry room is conveniently located on the main floor too! There is another over 1500 square feet in the unfinished basement ready for you to expand this home and double it's size. The 3-car garage opens up to an expanded driveway with plenty of parking spaces. Schedule a showing today!
